<p>Well, as it is not compiled/packaged by eZ Systems, I've decided a few week ago to create my own <a href="http://mxcl.github.com/homebrew/" target="_blank">homebrew</a>
 formula to install it on Mac OS X in one command line... I've also submitted a few other formulas to easily install this apps/libs on Mac OS X :&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/mxcl/homebrew/blob/master/Library/Formula/phpmyadmin.rb" target="_blank">phpMyAdmin</a>
